---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Save Editor Online"
  description="Privacy Policy for Save Editor Online. Learn how we handle your data."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> December 6, 2025
      </p>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to Save Editor Online ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your
          privacy and ensuring you have a safe experience on our website. This Privacy Policy
          explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 my-6">
          <p class="font-bold text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200">Key Takeaway:</p>
          <p class="text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">
            We are a client-side tool. Your save files are processed entirely within your web
            browser and are <strong>never uploaded to our servers</strong>. We do not have access to
            your game data.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Game Save Files:</strong> When you use our editor, you select files from your device.
            These files are loaded into your browser's memory for editing. They are NOT transmitted to
            us.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Communication:</strong> If you contact us via email or our contact form, we collect
            your email address and the content of your message to respond to your inquiry.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
        <p>
          When you visit our website, we and our third-party partners may collect certain
          information automatically, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Log Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, referring/exit pages,
            and timestamps.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on pages, and other interaction data.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cookies:</strong> Small text files stored on your device (see our Cookie Policy).
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>To operate and maintain the website.</li>
          <li>To improve user experience and website performance.</li>
          <li>To analyze usage trends and traffic (via Google Analytics).</li>
          <li>To display personalized advertisements (via Google AdSense).</li>
          <li>To protect against malicious activity and abuse.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use trusted third-party services that may collect and process data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>
            <strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website traffic analysis. Google operates independently
            and has its own privacy policy.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Google AdSense:</strong> For displaying advertisements. Google uses cookies to serve
            ads based on your prior visits to our website or other websites.
          </li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> For content delivery, security, and DDoS protection.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Your Rights (GDPR & CCPA)</h2>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5.1 GDPR (European Users)</h3>
        <p>If you are located in the EEA, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data.</li>
          <li>Object to processing or request restriction of processing.</li>
          <li>Data portability.</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5.2 CCPA (California Users)</h3>
        <p>If you are a California resident, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Request disclosure of personal information collected.</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal information.</li>
          <li>
            Opt-out of the sale of personal information (We do not sell your personal information).
          </li>
          <li>Non-discrimination for exercising your rights.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our service is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect
          personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child
          has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by
          posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:privacy@saveeditor.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline"
            >privacy@saveeditor.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
